1
00:00:01,400 --> 00:00:02,600
Hey, look, look, look!

2
00:00:02,740 --> 00:00:03,140
Huh?

3
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:04,200
Look at this.

4
00:00:04,270 --> 00:00:05,270
This is insane.

5
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:08,140
Sensei.

6
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:09,480
It's this...

7
00:00:09,740 --> 00:00:10,580
These comments on Vinsta.

8
00:00:10,580 --> 00:00:12,000
(New menu? What's new? It's all ripped off from other recipes.)
(And she has the nerve to teach cooking? What a joke.)

9
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:12,750
(All plagiarized recipes. Zero originality.)

10
00:00:12,750 --> 00:00:13,750
I...

11
00:00:14,010 --> 00:00:15,950
I'll take whatever revenge
Reika-san dishes out.

12
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:17,620
If it helps appease Reika-san,

13
00:00:17,780 --> 00:00:19,220
even just a little...

14
00:00:19,650 --> 00:00:21,420
I'm willing to endure anything,
no matter how cruel.

15
00:00:22,390 --> 00:00:23,520
I have to be open

16
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:25,430
to differing opinions.

17
00:00:26,060 --> 00:00:27,060
But...

18
00:00:27,290 --> 00:00:28,560
Reika-san, I'm sorry.

19
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:31,870
If your revenge against me
goes too far...

20
00:00:32,130 --> 00:00:33,770
...my dad might find out.

21
00:00:34,470 --> 00:00:36,340
And you'll be in danger.

22
00:00:36,970 --> 00:00:38,540
So I'll do my best to minimize

23
00:00:39,010 --> 00:00:40,170
any trouble that comes my way.

24
00:00:42,610 --> 00:00:45,310
My recipes are a culmination
of my own experiences

25
00:00:45,310 --> 00:00:47,080
and original ideas.

26
00:00:47,350 --> 00:00:48,780
They're all original.

27
00:00:48,980 --> 00:00:50,720
I can say that with a clear conscience.

28
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:58,360
One look
at this recipe notebook

29
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:59,860
should make that clear.

30
00:01:10,140 --> 00:01:11,140
Everyone...

31
00:01:11,270 --> 00:01:12,340
...is asking for a refund.

32
00:01:13,940 --> 00:01:15,240
That's their decision to make,

33
00:01:16,140 --> 00:01:17,810
and there's nothing I can do about it.

34
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:19,140
Also...

35
00:01:19,250 --> 00:01:21,680
The TV appearance
that was already booked...

36
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:24,450
They contacted us
and asked us to cancel...

37
00:01:24,620 --> 00:01:25,620
If this is the extent of it,

38
00:01:26,250 --> 00:01:27,250
it's nothing I can't handle.

39
00:01:28,690 --> 00:01:29,690
Ah!

40
00:01:31,460 --> 00:01:32,660
I don't care what happens to me.

41
00:01:33,390 --> 00:01:34,760
But if this escalates...

42
00:01:35,130 --> 00:01:37,000
...and my father finds out
Reika-san is behind this...

43
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,000
I...

44
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:39,570
I want to let her get her revenge.

45
00:01:40,430 --> 00:01:41,430
But...
